com.mavenproject.timescheduler.dialogs

Class ConsoleDialogBodyInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mavenproject.timescheduler.dialogs.ConsoleDialogBody
      • com.mavenproject.timescheduler.dialogs.ConsoleDialogBodyInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConsoleDialogBody

    public class ConsoleDialogBodyInfo
extends ConsoleDialogBody
    Trieda reprezentuje menu z informaciou. Pozostava z kratkeho textu s informaciou a otazky, ktora bude polozena uzivatelovi. Otazkou rozumieme typ textoveho vstupu, aky od uzivatela ocakavame. (y/s; ciselny vstup, textovy vstup, vyber moznosti, casovy udaj)
    See Also:
